s to be delivered from the UK.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Please do not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions in regards to the above announcement.</font></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; text-align: left; line-height: 16pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Kind regards,</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Steven Small</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Head Teacher</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Kingâ€™s School, Manila</span></p></font></div></span><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,